snippet.textDisplay:
I wonder what country is the one who sets up over 200 bio-labs around the world and conducts research on biological warfare and bio-terrorism using genetic engineering technology?

Shouldn’t Australia ask the WHO to investigate those bio-labs, instead?

Aren't there many doubts over those 200 bio-labs around the world - how many secrets is withheld by that country?
